title: Pakistan fight back to win the series
description: Jonathan Agnew is joined by Steven Finn, Ramiz Raja, Alex Hartley and Andy Zaltzman to reflect on the 3rd Test, and the series, as Pakistan fight back to win 2-1. We’ll also hear from England Head Coach Brendon Mccullum.
author: BBC Radio 5 Live
